</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.microsoft.com/globaldev/handson/user/IME_Paper.mspx" class="external text" title="http://www.microsoft.com/globaldev/handson/user/IME_Paper.mspx" rel="nofollow">What is an Input Method Editor and how do I use it?</a>, a Microsoft article about <a href="/wiki/Windows_XP" title="Windows XP">Windows XP</a>'s Input Method Editor.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.microsoft.com/globaldev/handson/user/xpintlsupp.mspx" class="external text" title="http://www.microsoft.com/globaldev/handson/user/xpintlsupp.mspx" rel="nofollow">Enabling International Support in Windows XP/Server 2003 Family</a>, a Microsoft tutorial on how to install input methods on <a href="/wiki/Windows_XP" title="Windows XP">Windows XP</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.typingchinese.com/Demo/Chinese_Input_DemoPageEn.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.typingchinese.com/Demo/Chinese_Input_DemoPageEn.htm" rel="nofollow">Tutorial on typing Chinese using PinYin method - based on HanWJ Chinese Inoput Engine</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.andante.org/ime.html" class="external text" title="http://www.andante.org/ime.html" rel="nofollow">IME Tutorial</a>, tutorial on how to use Microsoft Global IME for pre-<a href="/wiki/Windows_2000" title="Windows 2000">Windows 2000</a> systems.</li>
</ul>
